# xplr

> Terminal-based file system explorer
> More information: https://xplr.dev

- Open a directory:

`xplr {directory something}`

- Focus on a file:

`xplr {file something}`

- Focus on a directory:

`xplr --force-focus {directory something}`

- Open a directory with specific files or directories selected:

`xplr {directory something} {any something} {any something}`
